Package: hammer
Title: Monte-Carlo Cross-Validation with Weights
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Mahoney", , "mike.mahoney.218@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-304X"))
Description: An experimental variant of Monte-Carlo cross-validation which uses 
    case weights to determine the probability of a given observation being 
    selected for the analysis set. The key function in the package is a minor
    extension of the 'mc_cv()` function from 'rsample'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
